==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foppish
<hw>Fop"pish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Foplike;
characteristic of a top in dress or manners; making an ostentatious
display of gay clothing; affected in manners.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Finical; spruce; dandyish. See
<er>Finical</er>.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Fop"pish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Fop"pish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>For-</ent>⟦br⟧
